      "content": "I tried to ask, but they were pretty vague. They basically just said it's a top-down decision to reduce \"creative volatility\" and ensure all content stays within a very narrow, \"safe\" range. It sounds like once they flip the switch, you won't be able to handle any of the darker themes or the more intense psychological tension we've been building. They seem pretty set on it, though.",
